DEPENDENCIES
------------

+ eBox components

	+ libebox

+ Debian packages (apt-get install <package>)

	+ libdate-calc-perl
	+ libconfig-tiny-perl
	+ libsoap-lite-perl

+ modules from CPAN


INSTALLATION
------------

1.- Configure:

    $ ./configure <arguments>

    Accepts standard GNU configure arguments, run ./configure --help
    for a list

    Suggested argument: --localstatedir=/var/ , to have variable data
    installed in /var/lib/, instead of the default $prefix/var/lib/

2.- Installation, as root:

    $ make install
